title: President Donald J. Trump Signs S. 35 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Land & Agriculture	

Issued on:
May 25, 2018
On Friday, May 25, 2018, the President signed into law:S. 35, the “Black Hills National Cemetery Boundary Expansion Act,” which transfers administrative jurisdiction of approximately 200 acres of Federal land to the Department of Veterans Affairs for the Black Hills National Cemetery in the State of South Dakota.
